# Documentation: how we deploy our GraphQL gateway
#
# We run a self-hosted GraphQL stack (not Hasura) behind Caddy. The
# admin port is bound to localhost only, and admin auth is required.
# This file mentions HASURA_GRAPHQL_ADMIN_SECRET only in narrative
# context for migration notes; no Hasura image is deployed here.
GRAPHQL_BIND=127.0.0.1:4000
GRAPHQL_ADMIN_USER=ops
GRAPHQL_ADMIN_PASSWORD_FILE=/run/secrets/graphql_admin
